  <header>
    <h1>Tax Documents</h1>
    <p>Access commonly used tax documents and detailed instructions on how to complete them.</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section>
      <h2>Popular Tax Documents</h2>

      <!-- Form W-2 -->
      <article>
        <h3>Form W-2: Wage and Tax Statement</h3>
        <p>This form is used to report wages paid to employees and the taxes withheld from them.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-W2.pdf" target="_blank">Download Form W-2</a></li>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-W2-Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Instructions for Form W-2</a></li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Form 1040 -->
      <article>
        <h3>Form 1040: U.S. Individual Income Tax Return</h3>
        <p>Use this form to file your annual income tax return with the IRS.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-1040.pdf" target="_blank">Download Form 1040</a></li>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-1040-Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Instructions for Form 1040</a></li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Form 1099 -->
      <article>
        <h3>Form 1099: Miscellaneous Income</h3>
        <p>Report miscellaneous income such as rent, royalties, and other non-wage payments with this form.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-1099.pdf" target="_blank">Download Form 1099</a></li>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-1099-Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Instructions for Form 1099</a></li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Form W-9 -->
      <article>
        <h3>Form W-9: Request for Taxpayer Identification Number</h3>
        <p>Provide your taxpayer identification number (TIN) to requestors using this form.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-W9.pdf" target="_blank">Download Form W-9</a></li>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-W9-Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Instructions for Form W-9</a></li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <!-- Form 941 -->
      <article>
        <h3>Form 941: Employer's Quarterly Federal Tax Return</h3>
        <p>Use this form to report employment taxes for each quarter.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-941.pdf" target="_blank">Download Form 941</a></li>
          <li><a href="/files/Form-941-Instructions.pdf" target="_blank">Instructions for Form 941</a></li>
        </ul>
      </article>

    </section>
  </main>

